    loc : cssl-smt/src/predicate.rs + new module cssl-smt/src/lipschitz.rs
    scope :
      per-primitive Lipschitz rules :
        Sum      : Lip(f+g) ≤ Lip(f) + Lip(g)
        Product  : Lip(f·g) ≤ ||f||∞·Lip(g) + ||g||∞·Lip(f)
        Compose  : Lip(f∘g) ≤ Lip(f)·Lip(g)
        Constant : Lip(c) = 0
        Identity : Lip(id) = 1
      multi-dim Lipschitz (vector-input → vector-output)
      automatic @lipschitz-bound inference .via interval-arithmetic
      HIR-direct SMT translation (bypass text re-parse)
